{
  "stem": "617.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever there was, you know? and the officer and the ones-- like there was the-- this woman who I said that she was the manager.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, they were sleeping in the main house, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the higher ranking were watching us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were in the stables.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how many people were left at this point?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point, we were about 700 of us, at this point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were many stables.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was all of us, except the higher ranking ones were sleeping in the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next morning, after we tried to milk these cows, and we got something to eat, he gathered us all up, and he was holding an-- a zelapel, like, you know, counting us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was saying, look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, as you see, the SS have left, and I am watching you, but I have to leave, because my-- I want to go back to my family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't want to be-- become a prisoner of-- the Russians are approaching, and approaching very fast.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the German army is retreating, and they are going to go-- because this is a main highway, they are going to go through here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my advice to you is to go off on the fields, not on the main highways, because you'll find German soldiers, and you're going to be either shot, or caught, or taken on with them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So try and get on the fields.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was about seven of us who were friends at that time, my sister, and there were five-- there-- three of them were sisters, and two others, we decided we'd leave.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already getting a little bit dark at night that we leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The snow was deep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was January.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
